Package edu.cmu.lti.oaqa.pipeline

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AnswerExtractor
    This class use Abner named entity recognizer to extract certain phrases from the snippets we retrieved as the candidate answer.
    ComplexQueryConstructor
    This class gets each token of the query, then use wordNet to retrieve all synonyms of the token, and store them in complexQueryConcept.
    ConceptRetrieve
    This class retrieves concepts related to the query, using apis provided by Mesh, Jochem, Uniprot, DiseaseOntology, etc
    Consumer  
    DocumentRetrieve
    This class retrieves documents related to the query, using apis provided by PubMed.
    InitialAnnotator  
    QueryCombiner
    This class extract all tokens and their synonyms from complexQueryConcept, and use AND, OR to combine all the words together as the FinalQuery.
    QuestionReader
    A simple collection reader that reads documents/questions from a directory in the filesystem.
    SnippetRetrieval  
    TripleRetrieve
